WEBVTT

00:06:57.960 --> 00:07:00.640
"What would you like to tell
the people of America?"

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:04.800
I was expecting blame.

00:07:06.520 --> 00:07:08.160
But she looked at me and said,

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.520
"Tell them, 'Thank you.'

00:07:13.960 --> 00:07:17.536
3,000 Americans came
to my husband's memorial.

00:07:17.560 --> 00:07:19.136
They did not know me,

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:20.480
but they wept with me.

00:07:22.280 --> 00:07:23.640
Tell them, 'Thank you.'"

00:07:27.200 --> 00:07:29.536
Thousands of people showed up,

00:07:29.560 --> 00:07:30.976
because unlike national news,